essential-emerging-artists-for-2023-radar-3372061">NME 100</a>校友将于 2 月 2 日通过 Island 发行他们的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-debut-album-prelude-to-ecstasy-release-new-single-on-your-side-listen-preorder-3528044">《Prelude To Ecstasy》</a> （<a href="https://tldp.lnk.to/preludetoecstasyPR" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订</a>）。它将收录 2023 年的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-shares-smashing-debut-single-nothing-matters-radar-3433299">《Nothing Matters》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-new-single-sinner-uk-tour-radar-3463558">《Sinner》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-share-new-single-my-lady-of-mercy-3511842">《My Lady Of Mercy》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-debut-album-prelude-to-ecstasy-release-new-single-on-your-side-listen-preorder-3528044#:~:text=The%20Last%20Dinner%20Party%20have,%2Fpre%2Dsave%20here).">《On Your Side》</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-intimate-variety-show-at-london-roundhouse-buy-tickets-3507689">他们将在首张专辑发行前夕（2 月 1 日）在伦敦 Roundhouse 举办一场头条秀</a>。该团体此前曾开玩笑说，这场演出“可能是历史性的”。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fthe-last-dinner-party-tickets%2Fartist%2F5395177" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里找到任何剩余的门票</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-hit-out-at-lads-for-posting-weird-shit-on-twitter-have-some-fucking-decorum-3557794">《最后的晚宴》的帖子猛烈抨击“小伙子们”在推特上发布“奇怪的狗屎”：“有一些他妈的礼仪”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
