 《前一天》开发商宣布意外关闭，尽管最终发布了游戏https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-day-before-developer-announces-surprise-shut-down-尽管-finally-releasing-game-3557780?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-尽管游戏终于发布，但开发者宣布意外关闭的前一天Ali ShutlerTue, 12 Dec 2023 10:08:10 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3557780 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/the-day-before@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="前一天" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/the-day-before@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/the-day-before@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/the-day-before@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/the-day-before@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/the-day-before@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/the-day-before@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这款所谓的 MMO 在四天前发布了抢先体验版</p><p>尽管最终发布的游戏首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-day-before-developer-announces-surprise-shut-down-despite-finally-releasing-game-3557780">，但“前一天”的帖子开发商还是宣布意外关闭</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/the-day-before@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="前一天" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/the-day-before@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/the-day-before@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/the-day-before@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/the-day-before@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/the-day-before@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/the-day-before@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在游戏进入抢先体验仅四天后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-day-before"><em>The Day Before</em></a>开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/fntastic">Fntastic</a>宣布突然关闭。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/best-games-2023-switch-xbox-playstation-pc-3551161">2023 年 20 款最佳游戏</a></strong></li></ul><p>该工作室在社交媒体上分享的一份 <a href="https://twitter.com/FntasticHQ/status/1734265789237338453" target="_blank" rel="noopener">声明</a>中表示， <em>《The Day Before》</em> “在财务上失败了”，开发商“缺乏资金”来继续。</p><p> <em>《前一天》</em>原定于 2022 年 6 月发布，后来被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/post-apocalyptic-mmo-the-day-before-delayed-until-2023-3220078">推迟到 2023 年 3 月 1 日</a>。今年年初， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-day-before-delayed-for-8-months-over-lack-of-trademark-3386677">Fntastic 透露，由于工作室未能为游戏名称注册商标<em>，《The Day Before》</em>将被推迟八个月</a>。随后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-day-before-delayed-after-developers-assured-no-more-delays-3528900">再次推迟</a>，最终于上周进入抢先体验阶段。它可以通过 Steam 以 39.99 美元（31.85 英镑）的价格购买，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-day-before-10000-negative-reviews-3557070">很快就积累了超过 10000 条负面评论</a>，而 Fntastic 要求玩家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-day-before-developer-issues-apology-ahead-of-release-3553874">不要指责他们“诈骗”。</a></p><p> <em>《前一天》</em>曾一度是 Steam 上最受欢迎的游戏，但很快就成为该平台有史以来评分最低的游戏。</p><p> “我们真的很想发布新补丁来展现游戏的全部潜力，但不幸的是，我们没有资金来继续这项工作，”Fntastic 表示，并确认工作室已关闭。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">官方声明。 <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/fntastic?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#fntastic</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/thedaybefore?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#thedaybefore</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/propnight?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#propnight</a> <a href="https://t.co/AKcRHeIaIW">pic.twitter.com/AKcRHeIaIW</a></p><p> - Fntastic (@FntasticHQ) <a href="https://twitter.com/FntasticHQ/status/1734265789237338453?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 12 月 11 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> “收到的所有收入都用于偿还我们合作伙伴的债务，”他们证实。 “值得注意的是，我们在开发过程中没有向公众收取任何资金；没有预订或众筹活动。我们不知疲倦地工作了五年，为这项运动倾注了心血、汗水和泪水。”</p><p>该声明接着表示<em>，The Day Before</em>和 Fntastic 的另一款游戏<em>Propnight</em>的未来“未知”，但服务器将暂时保持运行。 “如果我们没有达到您的期望，我们深表歉意。我们做了力所能及的一切，但不幸的是，我们错误地估计了我们的能力。制作游戏是一项极具挑战性的工作。”</p><p>在<em>《The Day Before》</em>的整个开发过程中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/studio-bosses-deny-the-day-before-is-a-scam-3388280">Fntastic 曾多次告诉粉丝，这款游戏不是骗局</a>，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-day-before-developer-defends-use-of-unpaid-volunteers-3258652">被迫为使用无偿“志愿者”进行辩护</a>，并被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-day-before-is-now-being-accused-of-ripping-off-call-of-duty-and-the-last-of-us-3393158">指控抄袭<em>《使命召唤</em>》和<em>《最后生还者》</em></a> 。该游戏最初被宣布为僵尸生存 MMO，但发布的游戏是一款撤离射击游戏。</p><p>自该声明发布以来， <em>《The Day Before》</em>已无法通过 Steam 购买，预告片也已从 YouTube 上撤下，Fntastic 首席执行官 Eduard Gotovtsev<a href="https://twitter.com/eduardgotovtsev/">似乎也</a>离开了社交媒体。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/le-sserafim">LE SSERAFIM</a>成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miyawaki-sakura">Sakura</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/le-sserafims-sakura-pretty-serious-animal-crossing-3557629">公开了她对游戏的热爱</a>，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/animal-crossing">《动物之森》</a>是她的最爱。</p><p>尽管最终发布的游戏首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-day-before-developer-announces-surprise-shut-down-despite-finally-releasing-game-3557780">，但“前一天”的帖子开发商还是宣布意外关闭</a>。</p> ;
