omic-area"><em>Money Heist</em></a><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/money-heist-korea-joint-economic-area"><em>韩国</em></a>），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/super-junior">超级少年的</a>Choi Si-Won， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/woori-the-virgin">Woori The Virgin the Virgin的</a></em>Sung Hoon等等。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/parasite-park-so-dam-battle-with-cancer-i-cried-every-day-3557703">“寄生虫”女演员公园So-dam在与癌症的战斗中：“我每天哭泣”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
